SIMPLE: rip_cord
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rip cord
<hw>Rip cord</hw>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Aeronautics)</fld> <def>A cord by
which the gas bag of a balloon may be ripped open for a limited distance
to release the gas quickly and so cause immediate descent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a cord which, when pulled, opens a
parachute.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ripe</ent>⟦br⟧
